data.description: JUST REDUCED!!!!  Again to help towards needed repairs. All Brick home and Location  is  close to the Medical center and ETSU.  Sits on a decent size lot . ,Lots of natural lighting , Open Floor Plan Fireplace in the great room to enjoy chilly nights. Master bedroom and Kitchen have sliding glass door to back side foyer entrance with Marble flooring Main level has 2 bedroom and 2 full bath. Basement has a small kitchen Living room bedroom and another full bath and can be fixed up as an in law suite .(Exterior entrance only) . Driveway is asphalted ,steep but at top a walk in level entrance . Lots of mature trees and a nice  cement deck area on back of home for entertaining and having picnics in own yard, Home is being ''SOLD AS IS ''  Buyers and Buyers agent are to confirm any and all measurements on rooms and know most info is taken from County records,
